Full Title: Formulaic Language Research Network=20
Short Title: FLaRN 2010 conference=20

Date: 23-Mar-2010 - 26-Mar-2010
Location: Paderborn, Germany=20
Contact Person: Irina Dahlmann
Meeting Email: flarn2010@uni-paderborn.de
